                                        <h3><span class="text-o-color-4"><strong>LA CLAUDIA<br/></strong> <span class="h5-fs"><strong>★★★<span class="h5-fs">★</span></strong></span></span></h3>
                                        <div class="s_hr pb32 pt8" data-name="Separator" data-snippet="s_hr">
                                            <hr class="w-100 mx-auto"/>
                                        </div>
                                        <p><span class="text-o-color-4">La Claudia invites you into a bright and contemporary environment, where soft colors and chic furnishings enhance your sense of well-being. Whether you are unwinding after an active day or enjoying a quiet morning with a view, this room brings together elegance, space, and serenity for an unforgettable stay.</span></p>
                                        <p><span class="text-o-color-4"><span class="fa fa-tv"/>&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;<span class="fa fa-bathtub"/>&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;<span class="fa fa-wifi"/>&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;<span class="fa fa-free-code-camp"/>&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;<span class="fa fa-coffee"/>&amp;nbsp; <span class="o_small-fs">and more</span></span><br/><br/></p>
                                        <p><a class="o_translate_inline btn btn-custom" href="/shop/*la-claudia*" style="color: #FFFFFF; background-color: rgb(176, 158, 150); border-width: 1px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-style: solid; ">Discover the room</a></p>
